# Images Directory

This directory stores all images used in the site.

## Structure

- `avatar/` - Profile pictures and avatars
- `blog/` - Blog post images organized by date (YYYY/MM/)
- `projects/` - Project screenshots and thumbnails

## Usage

### In Markdown (Blogs)
```markdown
# Local relative path (for development)
![描述](../../assets/images/blog/2025/12/example.jpg)

# With jsDelivr CDN (for production - faster loading)
![描述](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shoa-lin/shoa-site@main/assets/images/blog/2025/12/example.jpg)
```

### In HTML
```html
<!-- Local path -->
<img src="assets/images/avatar/profile.jpg" alt="Profile">

<!-- CDN -->
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/shoa-lin/shoa-site@main/assets/images/avatar/profile.jpg" alt="Profile">
```

## Guidelines

1. **Optimize images** - Compress to < 500KB when possible
2. **Use descriptive names** - e.g., `blog-post-screenshot.jpg` not `img1.jpg`
3. **Organize by date** for blog images: `blog/YYYY/MM/`
4. **Max file size**: 100MB (GitHub limit), recommend < 1MB per image
